======================================================================
  IRC-ABbot                                  version 0.0.1 beta
======================================================================

  IRC ~ Automated Babbling Bot

  How To Use:
    $ bundle install --path .bundle
    $ bundle exec rake irc:abbot:join IRC="irc.freenode.com" CHANNEL="#ruby" NICK="abbot"
======================================================================
  
  Current Features:
    [+] basic IRC Network, Channel Connector
    [+] YAML Config Support
    [+] Help ~ 'abbot: help'
    [+] Babbler ~ 'abbot: babble'
    [+] Quote
    [+] URL Un-Shortener
  
======================================================================

  Future Roadmap:
    [+] google
    [+] whois
    [+] nslookup
    [+] ycombinator
    [+] twitter
    [+] reddit
    [+] slashdot
    [+] stackoverflow
    [+] github

